* Zyber looked at the deer again but then looked at Rowdy, she knew that he 
was planning to shoot one for her but she wasn't suer if she wanted him to 
go to the trouble of it. She smiled at him....*

" I could not ask you do do something like that just for me, it would be to 
much trouble to ask of you."

* She spoke with truth and concern, he was being so nice, she couldn't ask 
him to go to the trouble for her to kill a deer.
She looked at the deer again and got to her feet, she sniffed the air and 
waged her tail a bit.
Her stomach growled again.*
